snippet.title: Slappy Board Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Blow off steam in Slappy Board! Immerse yourself in different themes with multiple scenarios. Keep calm or lose control, the choice is yours. 
But don't forget to have fun and SLAP!

Wishlist on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1714910/Slappy_Board/
Talk to us on Discord! https://discord.gg/cTBgzZDp5d
